<section>
<num>§ 3435.</num>
<heading> Receiver of stolen property triable before or after principal</heading>
<content>
<p class="indent0">A person charged with receiving or concealing stolen property may be tried either before or after the trial of the principal offender.</p>
</content>
<sourceCredit>(<ref>June 25, 1948, ch. 645</ref>, <ref>62 Stat. 831</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
